    "body": "From what I can tell, it should be enough to:\r\n\r\n- Rename `checkIfHardhatNetwork` to something like `checkIfDevelopmentNetwork`\r\n- Check if the result of `web3_version` *either* starts with `hardhatnetwork` or with `anvil`\r\n\r\nI'm also ok with making this change without tests, because we don't currently have them for this method, and doing it would imply a level of mocking that doesn't seem worth it to me.",
